HEADWORD: Screak
<hw>Screak</hw> <pr>(skr⟦emac⟧k)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Screaked</conjf>
<pr>(skr⟦emac⟧kt)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Screaking</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[Cf. Icel. <ets>skraekja</ets>
